The tuwangis in Mighty Frog Pond are getting a little hoppity. It's time to put them down.

Eliminate the {@LinkCreature:5#7#tuwangi warfroggers}, {@LinkCreature:5#8#keen hat tuwangis}, and {@LinkCreature:5#9#stonehammer tuwangis}.

Report to Zelia at the Tuwangi Garrison when mission is complete.

More of the violent tuwangis defeated. Check.

Keep up the great work!

If only someone would go out into the world and take care of things they said they'd take care of instead of reporting to me empty-handed.

Hmm? Oh, no, I certainly couldn't be talking about you.
